replies.body:
this guy is so right on all his points!
u deserve a {{item:2010}} 

1. high dmg toplane champs like {{champion:92}} feel pretty useless atm
like: why go Riven top if you can just pick something WAY more tanky that still deals the same amount (or even more) of dmg? like {{champion:6}} {{champion:266}} {{champion:86}} {{champion:122}} 
and vs tanks its just a free lose anyways cause even a tiny bit of armor makes you completely uselss and they can burst you down in one combo (yes ... tanks that burst someone down ... so fun) - like  {{champion:516}} {{champion:78}} or even something like tank {{champion:79}} 
oh! and lets not forget the abusive mages top that can build armor and still deal a shit ton of dmg - looking at you {{champion:112}} 

2. ever since the changed and nerfs {{item:3071}} went from a pretty good item to a pretty shitty items
it just took ppl quite a while to realize that even if you are a tanky champ - a champ where BC should be a core item - BC is kinda shit
thats why even the BC-core users switched to {{item:3078}}
BC just cant compete! TF is straight up better - and mainly because TF deals more dmg (ofc it does - Spellblade passive is busted and BC got 2 dmg nerfs ... less AD and less armor shred)
also: why did tanky champs get another option for a 20%cdr item by taking away the option for dmg-champs?
mages have 20% cdr options: {{item:3003}} {{item:3285}} {{item:3030}} 
Tanks have a 20% cdr option: {{item:3110}} {{item:3025}} 
20% cdr options that are kinda champ specific / AS based: {{item:3078}} {{item:3508}} {{item:3115}} 
and tanky fighters have 20% cdr options: {{item:3078}} {{item:3071}} {{item:3025}} 
and high dmg fighters have no good 20% cdr option now (only if they can build {{item:3078}} )
just make BC a better offensive item again - and make it better for melee champs so ADCs cant abuse it

3. the scaling cdr shard is complete ass xD
every shard gives you good stats even in the earlygame: AD/AP ( = the go to), AS ( = rly good for AA champs ofc), AR/MR ( = early resistances are RLY strong), HP ( = also scaling so early its not a lot but at least you have some bonus HP)
1% (! xD) cdr at lvl1 is basically not existent ... and you have to wait until LVL 18 to get 10%??? that is WAY to slow
you probably wont even reach lvl 18 in most games
so you have to wait the entire game so your stat shard actually does anything
in the meantime everyone else has some bonus stats since lvl 1
if they dont buff it / make it flat early cdr then this stat shard it dead on arrival
NO ONE will pick this shard! even champs like {{champion:92}} - a champ that is super dependent on cdr - wont pick it!
she needs cdr AS FAST AS POSSIBLE - so why the hell would you pick a shard that kicks in at lvl 18?

